Can run without docker.
## Requirements:
1.	Data/genome should have gff, gtf and fna files.
2.	Change the name of paired end reads files –
for file in *_1.fastq.gz; do mv "$file" "${file/_1.fastq.gz/_R1.fastq.gz}"; done
for file in *_2.fastq.gz; do mv "$file" "${file/_2.fastq.gz/_R2.fastq.gz}"; done
3.	Give sample info file in data/sampleinfo.txt
4.	Download and gzip -d genome files.
5.	Download raw reads in the data/raw.
6.	Keep all the scripts in main directory.
7.	Make sure that all the files are executable. #chmod +x filename

 

